    <section>
        <h2>Internal Assessment Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
            A student is eligible for the internal assessment only if the attendance 
            percentage is greater than 75&#37;, the assignment count is less than 5 
            (&lt; 5), and the internal score is less than or equal to 40 (&le; 40).
        </p>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
